## Implementation Status

**COMPLETE** — All phases implemented and tested.

- Backend: 19/19 tests pass (test_fields, test_items, test_tables)
- Frontend: 8/8 tests pass (DataTable, FieldManager, ItemForm)
- Frontend builds successfully to `backend/static/`

